name: People of Bihar
overview:
PeopleofBihar.Com is a social networking website made for People of Bihar, Jharkhand, Eastern Uttar Pradesh who shares the common bloodline and common culture. It aims to bring all people of Bihar, Jharkhand, Eastern UP on a common platform irrespective of caste, creed, color, religion or gender. It aims to create an environment for development of India’s most glorious state Magadh(Bihar). Any one belonging to Bihar or connected to Bihar can join this website.

website(URL) : http://www.peopleofbihar.com
